beer.beer_description: A party of hops for our Party Wave IPA. Brewed for the launch of summer. Mosaic, Simcoe, Strata and a few of the C's join in. A modern IPA with a decent bitterness bite, malt backbone and stone fruit aroma.

items.badge_description: Celebrate women and non-binary folx in craft beer! Every year the Pink Boots Society (PBS) hosts Collaboration Brew Day where teams come together to brew a collab beer that supports the PBS mission to support, inspire, and encourage the professional development of women and non-binary people in the industry.
